# Postman Newman Framework with Jenkins

This repository automates Postman collections execution using Newman, generates test reports, and sends email notifications with the results.

## Features
- Executes Postman collections with Newman.
- HTML report generation.
- Jenkins pipeline to automate testing.
- Email notifications with total, passed, and failed test cases.

## Setup
1. Clone the repository
2. Install dependencies
    npm install
3. Execute tests
    npm test
## Jenkins Pipeline
- Add the `Jenkinsfile` to your Jenkins job.
- Configure the job with your repository.

## Reports
- View HTML reports in the `reports/` folder.

